query:
SELECT 
  i.id,
  i.type,
  i.status,
  i.result,
  i.createdAt,
  i.executedAt,
  pu.url as post_url,
  a.username as account_username
FROM interactions i
LEFT JOIN post_urls pu ON i.postUrlId = pu.id
LEFT JOIN accounts a ON i.accountId = a.id
WHERE i.type = 'like'
ORDER BY i.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 5
